  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/9f4dd5b084afab74a283a88ad571c261.avif?t=1695181191\" width=610 height=134 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/6648b7ebdc51cf39e929799ca2cee12c.poster.avif?t=1695181191\" width=610 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/6648b7ebdc51cf39e929799ca2cee12c.webm?t=1695181191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/6648b7ebdc51cf39e929799ca2cee12c.mp4?t=1695181191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>OA Family, a game with learning and relaxation. The main system of the game is to bring the popular English vocabulary game <strong>Hangman</strong> to do in a player-friendly format with a helper. There are cute images suitable for all ages. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/44699d571ab7bbafe816372fee2fcc35.poster.avif?t=1695181191\" width=610 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/44699d571ab7bbafe816372fee2fcc35.webm?t=1695181191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/44699d571ab7bbafe816372fee2fcc35.mp4?t=1695181191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are several help buttons to increase the fun and challenge.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/891ded2cec1af791acc2fbc1ea00fd3c.avif?t=1695181191\" width=610 height=134 /></span><br>Win the game to receive multiple random boxes for a chance to win special prizes.<br><br><br>The game also has an item collection and adventure system. <br>- Crafting system<br>- Weapon upgrade<br>- Cooking<br>- Fishing <br>and other systems that will be updated for players to enjoy it. <br><br><br>And most importantly, we will donate <strong>20%</strong> of our income <strong>without deducting expenses</strong> to children's charities in Thailand.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/1a40298643babd37ae604a53b8146b7a.poster.avif?t=1695181191\" width=610 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/1a40298643babd37ae604a53b8146b7a.webm?t=1695181191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/9f4dd5b084afab74a283a88ad571c261.avif?t=1695181191\" width=610 height=134 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/6648b7ebdc51cf39e929799ca2cee12c.poster.avif?t=1695181191\" width=610 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/6648b7ebdc51cf39e929799ca2cee12c.webm?t=1695181191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/6648b7ebdc51cf39e929799ca2cee12c.mp4?t=1695181191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>OA Family, a game with learning and relaxation. The main system of the game is to bring the popular English vocabulary game <strong>Hangman</strong> to do in a player-friendly format with a helper. There are cute images suitable for all ages. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/44699d571ab7bbafe816372fee2fcc35.poster.avif?t=1695181191\" width=610 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/44699d571ab7bbafe816372fee2fcc35.webm?t=1695181191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/44699d571ab7bbafe816372fee2fcc35.mp4?t=1695181191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are several help buttons to increase the fun and challenge.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/891ded2cec1af791acc2fbc1ea00fd3c.avif?t=1695181191\" width=610 height=134 /></span><br>Win the game to receive multiple random boxes for a chance to win special prizes.<br><br><br>The game also has an item collection and adventure system. <br>- Crafting system<br>- Weapon upgrade<br>- Cooking<br>- Fishing <br>and other systems that will be updated for players to enjoy it. <br><br><br>And most importantly, we will donate <strong>20%</strong> of our income <strong>without deducting expenses</strong> to children's charities in Thailand.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/1a40298643babd37ae604a53b8146b7a.poster.avif?t=1695181191\" width=610 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570040/extras/1a40298643babd37ae604a53b8146b7a.webm?t=1695181191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
